data.revised_prompt: Generate an image of a futuristic, sleek, and friendly AI assistant avatar. The avatar, though void of a specific name, contains a blend of high-tech digital characteristics, alongside a warm and approachable persona. Envision the color palette to be minimalistic and consist of shiny blue luminescence, in conjunction with translucent holographic attributes which collectively establish the avatar's overall aesthetic. The backdrop of the avatar is a clean, modern workspace, serving as a contrast to the technical components of the avatar. The desired resolution is 4K, and the applied art style attributes should embody that of a professional digital art standard.
